column2: SELECT    m.RA_deg AS input_ra, m.DEC_deg AS input_dec,    n.objid as sdssm_objid, n.distance as sdssm_distance,    p.ra AS sdss_p_ra, p.dec AS sdss_p_dec,   dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as sdss_p_type, p.modelMag_r, p.petroRad_r, p.petroRadErr_r, p.petroR5#_r, p.petroR5#Err_r, p.petroR9#_r, p.petroR9#Err_r into mydb.MyTable_# from MyDB.LASER_ML_radec AS m    OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.RA_deg, m.DEC_deg, #) AS n   LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll AS p ON n.objid=p.objid
